## Cleanup

At box or empty queue: final ledger update + dashboard render + cycle report. **Never
self-merge** — PRs wait for human/CI. The schedule fires the next cycle.

**Retiring the recurring workflow** (not per-cycle): when the drain is decommissioned, run
**`team-forge:teardown`** — it removes the schedule/cron trigger first (so no further cycles fire),
archives the ledger, prunes worktrees, and removes the launcher + profiles + ephemeral state.
